<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">銘　鵺　道入</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">［あからくちゃわん　めい　ぬえ　どうにゅう］</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<list>
